---
title: Quick Berbere-Spiced Paneer Curry with Veggies & Rapid Rice
description: Pop your uggies on and grab a bowl of this rich, creamy, comforting curry. With golden cubes of paneer, spinach and capsicum,
this gently spiced dish is a delight from start to finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-tikka-paneer-curry-5877fed6.jpg
